data.description: Hurry, ALL BRICK 2 Story Beauty! No updates required. 3 Bed 3 Bath Living room, dinning room, eat in kitchen, laundry room, an office, study or flex room. Ready for cooking  in this beautiful kitchen most appliances to remain.   Hidden Perks electrical updated throughout, window seat added, shelves in primary bathroom, gutter guards, and a new front door. Contractor's Grade dehumidifier and encapsulation added to the basement (transferable warranty), also bracing added to the basement This home is stunning! Call your favorite realtor today and request a tour, you'll be glad you did.
